data.title: Top 10 Songs Produced by Timbaland
data.meta_description: As a producer, Timbaland has got quite a discography, producing hits for Missy Elliott, Beyoncé, Justin Timberlake, Jay-Z, and many more. Which hits especially stand out among his legendary production discography? We've picked out 10 that really embody his genius.
data.text:
Timbaland has been very busy during quarantine, launching the live battle series Verzuz with Swizz Beatz. What started as one Instagram Live battle in March 2020 between the two Grammy-winning record producers, turned into a regular series that is now a cultural phenomenon that's keeping people entertained at home during the COVID-19 pandemic.

As a producer, Timbaland has got quite a discography, producing hits for Missy Elliott, Beyoncé, Madonna, Justin Timberlake, Jay-Z, and many more. Which hits especially stand out among his legendary production discography? We've picked out 10 that really embody his genius. Check them out below!

"Are You That Somebody?" - Aaliyah (1998)

"Pony" - Ginuwine (1996)

"Work It" - Missy Elliott (2002)

"Promiscuous (feat. Timbaland)" - Nelly Furtado (2006)

"SexyBack (feat. Timbaland)" - Justin Timberlake (2006)

"Big Pimpin' (feat. UGK)" - Jay-Z (1999)

“The Way I Are (feat. Keri Hilson & D.O.E.)” - Timbaland (2007)

"One in a Million" - Aaliyah (1996)

"Cry Me a River" - Justin Timberlake (2002)

"Get Ur Freak On" - Missy Elliott (2001)
